    EditPortListCheckboxActivity, EditPortListSpinnerActivity

    public abstract class EditPortListActivity<ITEM_T extends DeviceConfiguration>
extends EditUSBDeviceActivity
    EditPortListActivity is a helper class that assists in managing configuration of lists of items associated with ports on a controller.
